model.hed: The Stars of ​*Scream Queens*​ Slayed the Red Carpet at Their Big Premiere

items.caption: The wait for *Scream Queens* is finally over! The much anticipated series premieres tonight, and the stars already took to the red carpet for their own celebration. Lea Michele, Emma Roberts, Nick Jonas, and more were all in attendance, and were *obviously* all dressed to the nines. Ariana Grande was MIA, but we can only imagine how amazing she would’ve looked posing with her costars. From sleek gowns, to statement accessories and tailored suits, see what the stars wore on their big night!

fields.caption: LOS ANGELES, CA - SEPTEMBER 21:  (L-R) Actors Jamie Lee Curtis, Evan Paley, Diego Boneta, Nasim Pedrad, Red Devil, Billie Lourd, Skyler Samuels, Keke Palmer, Emma Roberts, Lucien Laviscount, Nick Jonas, Lea Michele, Abigail Breslin and Glen Powell arrive at the premiere of FOX TV's "Scream Queens" at The Wilshire Ebell Theatre on September 21, 2015 in Los Angeles, California.  (Photo by Amanda Edwards/WireImage)

fields.name: Andrea Navarro
fields.bio:
__What sort of advice would you give your 18-year-old self?__ 
 
Don't beat yourself up over the small things. I promise all of your hard work will pay off!  

__What fashion item seems to always be on your shopping list?__  

You can never go wrong with a good black leather jacket.  

__Share a funny anecdote from a first job or internship.__  
I once rode three NYC subways in 90 degree weather carrying a $180k alligator coat. Super casual.
fields.title: Digital Producer
